descript.abstract: The political boundary datalayer is a 1:25,000 scale datalayer containing the boundaries of the 351 communities (cities and towns) in Massachusetts. The seaward boundary of coastal communities has been defined at mean high water in this datalayer. In ArcSDE are the layer TOWNS_ARC stores the line features, with attributes for boundary type (state outline, boundaries betrween towns, and coastline).
